      "title": "Strategy 3: Noise + Latent Warp (Maximum Consistency)",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "ADVANCED TEMPORAL COHERENCE\n\nWarps BOTH the latent AND the noise for maximum\ntemporal consistency. Based on 'How I Warped Your\nNoise' (arXiv:2410.16152).\n\n1. Connect video frames to MegaFlowEstimate\n2. Connect previous latent to both warp nodes\n3. FlowNoiseWarp output -> KSampler noise input\n4. LatentWarp output -> KSampler latent input\n5. noise_blend 0.85 = keep 85% warped noise"
      ],
      "color": "#1a0f2e",
      "bgcolor": "#0d0a1a"
    },
